I'm not sure what client you are using, but most likely it means that you are connected to 5 seeders of 3200 in the swarm.  There should also be number for peers (or leechers).  You will connect to peers (people who don't have the whole torrent) as well.  It will download the files in small parts from the seeders and peers you are connected to, so since you are only sending and receiving small parts it isn't necessary to have the whole file to share.  The seed number should (theoretically) go up when more people have the whole file, and more seeds means the downloads get faster for all the leechers.
